trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreateUserError> event is raised when an attempt to create a new user with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> control fails.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreateUserError>时尝试创建的新用户将引发事件<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard>控制失败。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs> class provides the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs.CreateUserError%2A> property to indicate the <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipCreateStatus> enumeration value that corresponds to the error that occurred.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs>类提供<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs.CreateUserError%2A>属性以指示<xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipCreateStatus>对应于所发生的错误的枚举值。

trans-unit.source: In the following example, when the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreateUserError> event is raised, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs.CreateUserError%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs> object is displayed in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label> control, `Label1`, to provide information on why the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreateUserError> event occurred.
trans-unit.target: 在下面的示例中，当<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreateUserError>引发事件时，<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs.CreateUserError%2A>属性<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs>对象显示在<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label>控件， `Label1`，以提供有关原因的信息<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreateUserError>发生事件。

trans-unit.source: The following is the .aspx file that can be used to run the preceding example.
trans-unit.target: 以下是可以用于运行前面的示例中的.aspx 文件。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Security.MembershipCreateStatus" /> object that describes the result of a <see cref="Overload:System.Web.Security.Membership.CreateUser" /> attempt.
trans-unit.target: 描述 <see cref="T:System.Web.Security.MembershipCreateStatus" /> 尝试结果的 <see cref="Overload:System.Web.Security.Membership.CreateUser" /> 对象。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating the result of a <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreatingUser" /> event.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置指示 <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreatingUser" /> 事件结果的值。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs.CreateUserError%2A> property indicates the <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipCreateStatus> enumeration value that corresponds to the error that occurred during the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreatingUser> event.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs.CreateUserError%2A>属性指示<xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipCreateStatus>对应于期间出现的错误的枚举值<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreatingUser>事件。

trans-unit.source: The following example uses the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreateUserError> event to display the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs.CreateUserError%2A> property value in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label> control, `Label1`.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例使用<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreateUserError>事件以显示<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs.CreateUserError%2A>中的属性值<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label>控件， `Label1`。

trans-unit.target: 可以使用要运行该示例的.aspx 文件，请参阅<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs>主题。
